`вҳ… Insight в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ`
- The circular dependency trap when building barrel-based subpackages: if `checker.ts` imported from `./index` and `index.ts` re-exported from `./checker`, Node's module resolution creates a circular chain. The fix is simple вҖ” let `checker.ts` import directly from `./core` and `./world`, keeping the barrel as a one-way aggregator.
- The three new achievement types (`chunksVisited`, `biomesDiscovered`, `spiritsDiscovered`) required zero new store actions because the game already tracked `discoveredZones`, `visitedZoneTypes`, and `discoveredSpiritIds` for other systems. The `PlayerStats` interface is a clean seam that lets the achievement system compose from multiple store fields at check time.
